Arsenal legend, Paul Merson, has predicted the outcome of the Premier League match-day 35 fixtures taking place this weekend. Everton will host Chelsea in a Premier League tie at Goodison Park on Sunday, while Newcastle United will face Liverpool on Saturday afternoon. Tottenham Hotspur will clash with Leicester City on Sunday afternoon, while West Ham United will host Arsenal on Sunday evening. Providing his predictions, Merson was quoted by Sportskeeda as saying: Newcastle United 1-3 Liverpool
Watford 0-1 Burnley
Southampton 2-2 Crystal Palace
Aston Villa 3-0 Norwich City
Wolverhampton Wanderers 1-1 Brighton & Hove Albion
Leeds United 0-3 Manchester City
Tottenham Hotspur 3-0 Leicester City
Everton 1-1 Chelsea
West Ham United 0-2 Arsenal
Manchester United 2-2 Brentford